{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>救護員接報到場，證實事主明顯死亡，警方將安排為她驗屍確定死因。據悉，事主有身體病紀錄。</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260429/1126265437407940608479621.jpeg/XJLQ5CcWmeF0qEXulhevcLRN7UpbD1-67RMOAu0TDgI\"></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T13:38:34.316308+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":43,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}